room_title: Escape room "Escape the 90's" by EpIQ Escapes in Jackson (MI)

room_title: Escape room "Escape the 90's" by EpIQ Escapes in Jackson (MI)
review: This was a lot of fun - we did the 90's themed room, and our Gamemaster was super nice and helpful :) For people who love to think, this is way better than mindlessly watching a movie and costs about the same!

room_title: Escape room "Escape the 90's" by EpIQ Escapes in Jackson (MI)
review: We went for a teenager's birthday in the escape from the 90s room and absolutely loved it. The staff were very professional and very super friendly and helpful. Would definitely come back again. Our guide Shane was terrific and lighthearted. They put a lot of time, dedication, passion and effort into these rooms.
